他说"克莱尔  我整个总统工作目标很简单
He said, "Claire, my entire presidential agenda, it's very simple.

20
00:00:56,500 --> 00:00:59,960
我想看着每一个美国人的眼睛
I want to be able to look every single American in the eye,

21
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:02,330
知道自己让他们过得更好了"
and know that I have made their lives better."

22
00:01:03,050 --> 00:01:03,860
请讲
Yes.

23
00:01:04,990 --> 00:01:06,330
我得说  安德伍德夫人
I have to say, Mrs. Underwood,

24
00:01:06,330 --> 00:01:08,250
我觉得您很有魅力
I find you very charming.

25
00:01:08,880 --> 00:01:10,580
看起来也很诚实
And you seem quite honest.

26
00:01:11,170 --> 00:01:12,940
但我无法相信
But I have trouble believing

27
00:01:12,940 --> 00:01:15,480
您丈夫真的关心人民
that your husband truly cares about people.

28
00:01:16,240 --> 00:01:19,310
弗兰西斯·安德伍德是个好人
Well, Francis Underwood is a good man.

29
00:01:19,570 --> 00:01:22,000
他甘于奉献  慷慨大方
He's dedicated and generous.

30
00:01:22,290 --> 00:01:24,750
我有28年的亲身经历为证
And I have 28 years of proof.

31
00:01:24,750 --> 00:01:27,840
而且我可以说  即使我没嫁给他
And I can honestly say, even if I wasn't married to him,

32
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:30,020
也会投票给他
he would definitely have my vote.

33
